Canada Cooperatives Act
SubjectRegulations Amending Certain Department of Industry Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending CERTAIN DEPARTMENT OF INDUSTRY REGULATIONS, which include the Canada Business Corporations Regulations, 2001 and the Canada Cooperatives Regulations in order to address issues raised as a result of comments from the Standing Joint Committee of the Senate and House of Commons for the Scrutiny of Regulations and to be inclusive of common and civil law terminology.
